channel.title: Hamachi Prememium Trial - RAN OUT! SHIT!
channel.description:
OK so I'm putting off this "Your Hamachi Premium Account Expires In..." what ever a few days. So I'm asked about my network on MSN, I give him the info, and ... he says IT says "SHIT, I am out of premium time."
I have a wireless router, and Hamachi just came easier.
My dad isn't so big on me and the internet, so he refuses to get me a wireless router. I'm on a laptop, and he's gone back to dial-up. One night I'm like "damn I'm bored" ... so I turn on my computer. Apparently it already has a router or something, and WALA, it picks up my neighbor's internet!
So, when I try to get into the router, I need the username and the password. Obviously these arn't mine, so I try the usual admin and password, admin and admin etc.. I get into the router one day, and than after I add my network, it asks me again, and then it says the router doesn't exist :eek:
Anyway I work it out, I can't use No-IP or Hamachi, wtf am I gonna do :|
